*hamcrest-0.1.0_p20160709 (29 Aug 2016)

  29 Aug 2016; Amadeusz Żołnowski <aidecoe@gentoo.org>
  +hamcrest-0.1.0_p20160709.ebuild:
  Bump version to latest

  Latest revision a857893 from upstream repo has been packed and uploaded
  to dev.gentoo.org, because upstream still doesn't make releases. This
  version includes fixes for which previous version needed to be patched,
  so as soon this one is stable, older version can be removed.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.3.0

